ingredients.ingredient: 1 package Duncan Hines® Golden Yellow Cake Mix

cookingTips: Use a cake mix as base for quick, easy muffins with reliable results and consistent crumb
Mix oats into batter to add hearty texture and nutty flavor without developing gluten
Fill muffin cups evenly and bake at the temperature specified on the cake mix package
enrichment.coachingPrompt: Help the user make quick, easy muffins by combining a cake mix base with oats for added texture, mixing gently to avoid overdeveloping gluten, and baking until golden.
